
'''觀光業'''是[[克羅埃西亞|克羅埃西亞]]的主要產業之一。2012年，克羅埃西亞有1180萬人的國際遊客<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mmtpr.hr/default.asp?id=1627|title=HRK 6 Billion to be invested in new tourist season|year=2006|accessdate=2008-02-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071118030756/http://www.mmtpr.hr/default.asp?id=1627|archivedate=2007-11-18}}</ref>。2013年，這一數字超過1400萬人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mint.hr/UserDocsImages/htz-turizam-br012_HR.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-12-25 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131225213237/http://www.mint.hr/UserDocsImages/htz-turizam-br012_HR.pdf |archivedate=2013-12-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://press.croatia.hr/Documents/3030/Dolasci-i-nocenja-turista-sijecanj-PROSINAC-2013-2012.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-02-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222000137/http://press.croatia.hr/Documents/3030/Dolasci-i-nocenja-turista-sijecanj-PROSINAC-2013-2012.pdf |archivedate=2014-02-22 }}</ref>。克羅埃西亞定下了2020年觀光客數達到1750萬人，觀光業收益達170億美元的目標<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.poslovni.hr/hrvatska/cilj-je-udvostruciti-potrosnju-do-2020-251012|title=Cilj je udvostručiti potrošnju do 2020.|work=Poslovni dnevnik|accessdate=9 June 2015|archive-date=2020-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200807102059/https://www.poslovni.hr/hrvatska/cilj-je-udvostruciti-potrosnju-do-2020-251012|dead-url=no}}</ref>。克羅埃西亞全國有八個國家公園。2005年，[[孤獨星球|孤獨星球]]將克羅埃西亞選為最佳觀光目的地<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lonelyplanet.com/press-centre/press-release.cfm?press_release_id=159|title=Press releases – Press – Lonely Planet|author=Lonely Planet|publisher=|accessdate=9 June 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100521000955/http://www.lonelyplanet.com/press-centre/press-release.cfm?press_release_id=159|archive-date=2010-05-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2006年，國家地理雜誌也將克羅埃西亞選為最佳旅遊目的地<ref>Jon Bowermaster, [http://www.nationalgeographic.com/adventure/0511/features/croatia.html Destination of the Year: Exploring the New Croatia] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nationalgeographic.com/adventure/0511/features/croatia.html |date=20071112051707 }}</ref>。2014年，克羅埃西亞主要國外遊客客源如下<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://business.croatia.hr/Documents/3675/Tourism-in-Figures-2014.pdf |title=Tourism in Figures 2014 |accessdate=2016-02-02 |archive-date=2015-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151216034314/http://business.croatia.hr/Documents/3675/Tourism-in-Figures-2014.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref>：
